        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="大部分以尚硅谷学习路线"><a href="#大部分以尚硅谷学习路线" class="headerlink" title="大部分以尚硅谷学习路线"></a>大部分以尚硅谷学习路线</h1><h2 id="大处着眼"><a href="#大处着眼" class="headerlink" title="大处着眼"></a>大处着眼</h2><p><a href="%5B%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7Java%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B(%E5%9C%A8%E7%BA%BF%E7%AD%94%E7%96%91+Java%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E7%9C%9F%E9%A2%98)_%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9_bilibili%5D(https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Kb411W75N?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0)">Java基础部分</a> –&gt; <a href="%5BMySQL%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1%E6%9D%BF%EF%BC%8Cmysql%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%88%B0mysql%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%81%E7%A1%AC%EF%BC%81_%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9_bilibili%5D(https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1iq4y1u7vj?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0)">Mysql基础</a> –&gt; <a href="%5B%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7JDBC%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%B7%E5%B8%88%E5%82%85%E5%B8%A6%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%99%E5%BC%8F%E6%90%9E%E5%AE%9Ajdbc%EF%BC%89_%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9_bilibili%5D(https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1eJ411c7rf?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0)">JDBC核心技术</a> –&gt;<a href="%5B%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B72022%E7%89%88Maven%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%88maven%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8+%E9%AB%98%E6%B7%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%BD%91%E6%97%A0%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%B3%EF%BC%81%EF%BC%89_%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9_bilibili%5D(https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV12q4y147e4?p=14&spm_id_from=pageDriver)">maven</a>–&gt; <a href="%5B%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%E4%B8%A82022%E7%89%88JavaWeb%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B(%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A0%88,%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98)_%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9_bilibili%5D(https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1AS4y177xJ?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0)">javaweb</a> –&gt;<a href="%5B%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7Spring%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%88spri